, and find none of them\nare associated with young stars. This sets challenges to the previously\nproposed scenario of triggered star formation by SNR shocks in IC~443.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 30 Oct 2022 18:17:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 26 Nov 2022 07:12:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-29"}
