h the quenched fraction measured both for the MW/M31 system\nand from the ELVES survey. We discuss the implications of our results for the\nformation and evolution of low-mass galaxies, and for the stellar mass\nfunctions of low-mass galaxies to be observed at high redshift.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 31 Oct 2022 10:08:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 1 Nov 2022 01:46:54 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 21 Dec 2022 14:50:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-16"}
