arious GNN benchmarks demonstrate that our approach\nachieves superior performance over de facto baselines with more than 95.8% cost\neduction in a fast convergence speed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 31 Oct 2022 13:03:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-01"}
