 in northern Italy,\nand spanning a month in summer 2014), and use the posterior pdf of the\nparameters as a starting point to perform an Uncertainty Quantification\nanalysis on groundwater travel-time distributions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 31 Oct 2022 15:14:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 14 Mar 2023 15:45:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-15"}
