er, we propose a\nlightweight refinement method following an \"expand-replace\" manner to further\noptimize the top-$n$ result with little overhead, and we extend our solution to\nsupport CKS with multiple query nodes. We also analyze our solution's\neffectiveness theoretically. Comprehensive experimental studies on various\nreal-world datasets demonstrate our method's superiority.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 31 Oct 2022 15:37:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 24 Dec 2022 01:47:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-27"}
